{"type":null,"faqId":48002,"title":"Mate S_手机使用过程中有时没有声音，怎么办？","answer":"1.请注意是否有使用蓝牙耳机或者B2手环等外接音频设备，导致声音从外接设备发出而手机喇叭不出声。\n2.有些应用声音设置是从听筒出声，如微信聊天，语音信息可以设置从听筒出声（设置-聊天-使用听筒播放声音），而听筒相比喇叭的声音会比较小，有时会误以为没有声音。\n3.插上耳机声音是否能从耳机出来，如果耳机使用正常，那就属于喇叭硬件损坏，建议去网点维修更换。","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":2,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3588","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445591281000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":137,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}